  <h4>Form content</h4>

  <p>A user will have a better experience with submitting a form if the elements are easy for them to identify and move between.</p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Text label</strong> - Use to identify form elements that are required or recommended.</li>
    <li><strong>Popover</strong> - Use to display helpful information near form elements that may need more explanation beyond text labels.</li>
    <li><strong>Form field or Select list</strong> - Use to write text or make a selection from a list.</li>
    <li><strong>Placeholder text</strong> - Use within a form field or select list as an example of how to correctly provide an input.</li>
    <li><strong>Helper text</strong> - Use underneath a form element as an example of how to correctly provide an input.</li>
  </ul>

  {% call components.example(palette='lightest') %}
